% (rectangle) -18 118 placeBR
% (right) 35 138 placeBL
% (rectangle) 35 130 placeBL
% (trapezoid) 

TR (left rectangle) -20 20 placeSL
(right rectangle) 40 20 placeSL
(trapezoid) 10 20 placeSL

showpage

